  ('optician-moex-00103', 'optician', 'optician-moex-114-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那種材質不是親水的？', '["甲基丙烯酸（Methacrylicacid,MAA）", "矽（Silicone）", "聚乙烯醇（Polyvinylalcohol,PVA）", "甲基丙烯酸羥乙酯（Hydroxyethylmethacrylate,HEMA）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b70d36ef6657", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5101fd87d88e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00104', 'optician', 'optician-moex-114-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於矽氧烷丙烯酸酯（siliconeacrylate）硬式隱形眼鏡添加氟（fluorine）的好處，下列何者錯誤？', '["可降低沉積物堆積", "可增加表面潤濕性（surfacewettability）", "可降低淚膜破裂時間（tearbreakuptime）", "可增加透氧性（oxygentransmissibility）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b70d36ef6657", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5101fd87d88e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00105', 'optician', 'optician-moex-114-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於隱形眼鏡的透氧率（oxygenpermeability,Dk）和傳氧率（Oxygentransmissibility,Dk/t）何者正確？', '["隱形眼鏡的透氧率和鏡片的厚度有關", "隱形眼鏡的透氧率和鏡片的大小有關", "隱形眼鏡的傳氧率和鏡片的厚度有關", "隱形眼鏡的傳氧率和鏡片的大小有關"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b70d36ef6657", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5101fd87d88e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00106', 'optician', 'optician-moex-114-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於硬式隱形眼鏡材質，下列何者正確？', '["矽／丙烯酸酯（Silicone/Acrylate）是第一種硬式隱形眼鏡的材質", "氟矽／丙烯酸酯（Fluoro-Silicone/Acrylate）材質比起矽／丙烯酸酯更濕潤（wettable），因此戴起來比較舒服", "比起近視眼，遠視眼更不需要使用高透氧的氟矽／丙烯酸酯材質的硬式隱形眼鏡", "高透氧的氟矽／丙烯酸酯材質比起低透氧的氟矽／丙烯酸酯材質硬式隱形眼鏡耐刮"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b70d36ef6657", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5101fd87d88e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
